# Bismuth UI Foundations

This pen anchors Bismuth-native design artifacts for reuse inside Bismuth.

## Source Canvas

- `design/bismuth-ui-foundations.canvas`

## Token contract

- `color.surface` + `color.accent` are the canonical shell + call-to-action color tokens.
- `space.2`, `space.3`, and `radius.md` are baseline spacing/radius values for component parity.
- Mode behavior is controlled by `designSystem.activeTokenMode` and resolved through MCP handoff tooling.

## Component contract

- `Button/Primary/MD` is the baseline CTA component variant.
- `Shell/Sidebar` mirrors current app-shell ergonomics and should remain mapped to `src/lib/ui/sidebar-shell.svelte`.

## Implementation notes

- Use `reorder_canvas_elements` to maintain deterministic layer stacks during template updates.
- Use `set_canvas_token_mode` before exporting handoff artifacts for theme-specific outputs.
- Use `generate_code_connect_snippets` to produce framework-targeted snippets for implementation handoff.
